div1.p:
The prisoner had nothing to say in his defence, but call'd Mr. Spurier, who had known him about three years; Mr. Norman, between three and four; Mr. Ashton, six or seven; Mr. Leyfort, six or seven; Mr. Caruthas, eight; Mr. Luallin. between two and three;
Samuel Guest
, about eleven; and Mrs. Neves, five weeks; who all gave him a good character.
